======================================================================
IHARA ZETA DETERMINANT: Z(u)^{-1} = det(I - u*A)
======================================================================

  p=7, Paley:
  Eigenvalues: ['3.00+0.00j', '-0.50+1.32j', '-0.50+1.32j', '-0.50-1.32j', '-0.50+1.32j', '-0.50-1.32j', '-0.50-1.32j']
  Z(0.1)^{-1} = det(I - 0.1*A) = 0.983450
